# Imperial Foundation CDC

Community development platform for the Imperial Foundation Community Development Corporation (IFCDC).

## Technology Stack

- **Frontend**: React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui, Vite
- **Backend**: Express.js, Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL
- **Services**: Stripe, Twilio, OpenAI (AURA AI), WebSockets

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install
cp .env.example .env   # Configure DATABASE_URL, JWT_SECRET, etc.
npm run db:push
npm run dev
```

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Start development server |
| `npm run dev:client` | Start Vite client only (port 5000) |
| `npm run build` | Production build |
| `npm run start` | Run production server |
| `npm run check` | TypeScript type check |
| `npm run db:push` | Push Prisma schema to database |

## Project Structure

```
├── client/          # React frontend
├── server/          # Express API
├── prisma/          # Database schema
├── shared/          # Shared types and schemas
└── script/          # Build scripts
```

## Environment Variables

- `DATABASE_URL` — PostgreSQL connection string
- `JWT_SECRET` — JWT signing secret
- `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` — Stripe API key
- `OPENAI_API_KEY` — AURA AI integration
- `TWILIO_*` — SMS notification credentials
